{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/urban-aboriginal-ministry/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"ffeb34ba-35fa-56e4-a2ce-9d81868b65a4","html":"<p>The  Urban Aboriginal Ministry is a ministry of the Anglican Parish of St. Mary Magdalene in the Greater Vancouver Area to the First Nations people and their loved ones. The Ministry provide medicine wheel circles with smudging for all occasions (on request) and cultural funerals and weddings. It hosts Annual Feasts on Christmas, Easter and Thanksgiving. They also provide cultural gatherings where they teach arts &#x26; crafts such as drum making to restore the traditional ancestral teachings. The UAM responds to calls for practical needs such as food, furniture, clothing and transportation.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#digital-outreach\">Digital Outreach</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#executive-advisory-board-functions\">Executive Advisory Board Functions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#sumdging-ceremony\">Smudging Ceremony</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"digital-outreach\"><a href=\"#digital-outreach\" aria-label=\"digital outreach permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Digital Outreach</h2>\n<p>My principal role as the digital communications officer is to build and maintain the new website.\nIt has been set up on Bluehost for now and runs on a wordpress blog.  The site is a collective\nproject. Images are gathered by others and posted by myself.  We are looking for a content moderator.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://urbanaboriginalministry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Urban Aboriginal Ministry Site</a>.*</p>\n<h2 id=\"executive-advisory-board-functions\"><a href=\"#executive-advisory-board-functions\" aria-label=\"executive advisory board functions permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Executive Advisory Board Functions</h2>\n<p>We meet as an advisory board and review all of the activities of the ministry once per month.\nI report on my role as the website administrator and provide back up for other board members.</p>\n<h2 id=\"smudging-ceremony\"><a href=\"#smudging-ceremony\" aria-label=\"smudging ceremony permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Smudging Ceremony</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 600px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/88bb62809a91d62e13d6606243256147/82472/mainbanner.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/88bb62809a91d62e13d6606243256147/01472/mainbanner.webp 240w,\n/static/88bb62809a91d62e13d6606243256147/222bd/mainbanner.webp 480w,\n/static/88bb62809a91d62e13d6606243256147/965c5/mainbanner.webp 600w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/88bb62809a91d62e13d6606243256147/3bc27/mainbanner.jpg 240w,\n/static/88bb62809a91d62e13d6606243256147/98431/mainbanner.jpg 480w,\n/static/88bb62809a91d62e13d6606243256147/82472/mainbanner.jpg 600w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/88bb62809a91d62e13d6606243256147/82472/mainbanner.jpg\"\n          alt=\"mainbanner.jpg\"\n          title=\"mainbanner.jpg\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/urban-aboriginal-ministry/","tagSlugs":["/tag/design/","/tag/typography/","/tag/web-development/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-11-05T22:40:32.169Z","description":" The Urban Aboriginal Ministry is a ministry of St. Mary Magdelene Anglican Church and supports Prayer Circles, Four Annual Feasts: Easter, Thanksgiving, Winterfest, and Christmas, Traditional as well as Ceremonies and Pastoral Care.","tags":["Design","Typography","Web Development"],"title":"Urban Aboriginal Ministry","socialImage":"/media/mainbanner.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/urban-aboriginal-ministry/"}}}